                        <description><![CDATA[<p>The <code>paige/youtube</code> shortcode plays a YouTube video.</p>
<h2 id="basic">Basic</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">youtube</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;dQw4w9WgXcQ&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>























    























    


<div class="paige-shortcode-youtube">
    























<div class="paige-video ratio ratio-16x9" >
    






<iframe  allowfullscreen   referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"   src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?hl=en-us&amp;modestbranding=1"   title="YouTube video" ></iframe>

</div>

</div>

<h2 id="autoplay-parameter">Autoplay parameter</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">youtube</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">autoplay</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">true</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">video</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;dQw4w9WgXcQ&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>























    





    



















    


<div class="paige-shortcode-youtube">
    























<div class="paige-video ratio ratio-16x9" >
    






<iframe  allowfullscreen   referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"   src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?autoplay=1&amp;hl=en-us&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;mute=1"   title="YouTube video" ></iframe>

</div>

</div>

